data.description: This beauty located only 3 minutes from downtown Fountain Inn is worth the visit. Since being built in 2018, The home has been through a series of custom modifications to meet the owners pleasures. Here is an opportunity for you to reap the benefits without the expenses. They have installed natural gas to service the tankless water heater, heat pump and Stove making the home more energy efficient. As far as all the appliances go, they all stay with the home. Including the washer, dryer and as a BONUS the Sony Bravia that is mounted in the office space that was added on to the upstairs as one of the custom features. The Garage was transformed into a massive living room area, Great for entertainment. What better way to entertain yourself in the kitchen cooking up a great meal while listening to the plug and play music system installed in the ceiling. Laminate floor throughout the home, Custom dog house installed underneath the stair case, Under ground irrigation system, Storage building in the fenced in backyard and addition to the driveway for extra parking. The community also has a pool for you to enjoy, without you having to service it. As if it wasn't enough, the owners are also offering $5,000 in closing costs or to help buyers buy down their rate. Located only 5 minutes of 385 S. Don't miss out!!!! Schedule your private showing today!!!
